metadata.name: Demon Slayer Alexandra
metadata.description:
S - Class Demon Slayer, always accompanied by her Pegasus Aster.  She is not very quick, but she possesses superhuman strength. 

One day, a human opens the gate to multidimensional world where demons and ghost resides, out of sheer curiosity. The gate breaks and demons from all over the world are able to materialize themselves into a solid humanoid form and start to kidnap and kill human.

Because of that, demon slayers start to hunt them and create a game called “The Feast of Slayer” where they compete against each other and decides who is the best demon killer.

4000 px X 5216 px 300 DPI

Original artwork by Nickfilbert
